### UpdateQuantitys - Reportar consumo de pedido a BC

# Ejemplo 1: Actualizar cantidades de ensambles y componentes
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/EntryRequest/update-quantities?companyCode=COMPANY001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 10300,
  "entryRequestAssembly": [
    {
      "id": 4733021,
      "quantityConsumed": 1
    },
    {
      "id": 4733022,
      "quantityConsumed": 2
    },
    {
      "id": 4733023,
      "quantityConsumed": 1
    }
  ],
  "entryRequestComponents": [
    {
      "id": 12345,
      "quantityConsumed": 5
    },
    {
      "id": 12346,
      "quantityConsumed": 3
    }
  ]
}

